  "letters_page": "[DEVNOTE: *** INTRODUCTION_BEGIN ***\nNotes | first | villain | Thug Thatchar (Andrew Thatcher)\nNotes | first | Ruby (Ruby Mortensen, Thug's girlfriend)\nNotes | first | villain | death | Kulla\nJ. Jonah Jameson | villain | Milestone: (first)\nJohn Jameson | Milestone: (first)\nChameleon | villain | Milestone: (first)\n*** INTRODUCTION_END ***]\n[DEVNOTE: *** HIGHLIGHTS_BEGIN ***]\n[HANG0] * A mobster, a skyscraper, and a bucket of hot rivets walk into a Thor comic... and Odin's basically on standby.\n[HANG0] * Ant‑Man faces a disposable warlord, and I'm left feeling like the only one who served a prison sentence.\n[HANG0] * Spider‑Man stops a space disaster and still gets branded a menace.\n[HANG0] * FIXME - write something\n[DEVNOTE: *** HIGHLIGHTS_END ***]"
